@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.49
    v0 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.07 * v1 + 0.78)) * wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.66)))
    tmp = v0
    v2 = (wp.abs(v2) / v2)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v2 + 0.23 * v0 + 0.97)))
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.93)) / wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.78)))
    data[tid] = v0
